OL,3,CPrivate healthcare insurance costs
OL,4,Crising as record numbers pay for
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FThe cost of private healthcare
OL,8,Finsurance is rising as record numbers
OL,9,Fof people decide to pay for their
OL,10,Ftreatment, it has been reported.
OL,12,FBrokers have seen health insurance
OL,13,Fprice increases of about 25% in the
OL,14,Flast year, the i reports.
OL,16,FThis is due to an increase in the
OL,17,Fnumber of claims being made, and
OL,18,Fincreased medical costs, the paper
OL,19,Fadds.
