OL,3,CPrivate healthcare insurance costs
OL,4,Crising as record numbers pay for
OL,5,Ctreatment
OL,7,FRecord levels of people are using the
OL,8,Fprivate sector for their healthcare,
OL,9,Fwith 238,000 private hospital
OL,10,Fadmissions in the first three months
OL,11,Fof the year ` more than any previous
OL,12,Fquarter on record, according to
OL,13,Ffigures from the Private Healthcare
OL,14,FInformation Network (Phin).
OL,16,FAnd an unprecedented number of these
OL,17,Fwere paid for using insurance, rather
OL,18,Fthan the patient paying directly.
OL,20,FIt comes as the overall NHS waiting
OL,21,Flist stands at 7.6 million.
