OL,7,FDr Christopher Smith-Brown, a clinical
OL,8,Fadviser at the Phin, said: "Our data
OL,9,Fshows that record numbers of people
OL,10,Fare turning to the private sector for
OL,11,Ftheir healthcare and that the number
OL,12,Fusing private medical insurance is at
OL,13,Fan all-time high.
