OL,7,FHe said: "Employers are typically
OL,8,Fseeing their healthcare costs increase
OL,9,Fby 15 or 25% on policies renewing this
OL,10,Fyear. In rare cases, we have had some
OL,11,Fclients see premium increases of more
OL,12,Fthan 50% this year."
OL,14,FAnd Matt Fletcher, a senior health
OL,15,Finsurance broker at Globacare, said
OL,16,Fthat the cost of private health
OL,17,Finsurance schemes had risen by about
OL,18,F10 to 15%, but he had seen increases
OL,19,Fthat were higher this year.
